{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tipping-content-js","path":"/denmark","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Traditionally, tipping has not been common, but is being introduced by outside influences. Since service charges are automatically included in the bill at restaurants and hotels, and tips for taxi drivers and the like are included in the fare, tipping should be given only as a token of real appreciation for the service. The tips will most often be split between the waiters and the kitchen. Taxi drivers do not expect tips, any extra service (such as carrying bags) will be listed on the receipt according to rate. While tipping is not expected, nor required, tipping for outstanding service is obviously greatly appreciated.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/denmark","title":"Denmark","author":"Joni","date":"2019-11-20","image":"denmark.jpg"}},"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4053164556962026,"src":"/static/21f1317223636f9fbd582934ece1ea9f/90537/denmark.jpg","srcSet":"/static/21f1317223636f9fbd582934ece1ea9f/b3ebb/denmark.jpg 270w,\n/static/21f1317223636f9fbd582934ece1ea9f/95b54/denmark.jpg 540w,\n/static/21f1317223636f9fbd582934ece1ea9f/90537/denmark.jpg 1080w,\n/static/21f1317223636f9fbd582934ece1ea9f/3cda3/denmark.jpg 1620w,\n/static/21f1317223636f9fbd582934ece1ea9f/1f682/denmark.jpg 2160w,\n/static/21f1317223636f9fbd582934ece1ea9f/39233/denmark.jpg 5551w","sizes":"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"image":"denmark.jpg"}}}